comments: Banchero (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an Allen (CLE).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Wagner (ORL) loses control of the ball OOB.
Mobley (CLE) is in the lane for less than three seconds when Suggs (ORL) makes contact with the ball.
Suggs (ORL) makes marginal contact with Mitchell's (CLE) right arm before dislodging the ball away.
Garland (CLE) steps out of bounds with his right foot while making contact with the ball. The violation occurs prior to any potential contact by Suggs (ORL).
Wagner (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds prior to Garland (CLE) losing control of the ball.
Mobley (CLE) beats Bancharo (ORL) to the spot and absorbs the oncoming contact to his chest during Mobley's (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) and Wagner (ORL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Fultz (ORL) releases the in-bounds pass within 5 seconds.
On both free throws, Mitchell (CLE) releases the ball right at 10 seconds.
Fultz (ORL) attempts to commit a take foul on Garland (CLE) and marginal contact occurs.
Garland (CLE) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.

Wade (CLE) contests the shot and initiates contact with Wagner's (ORL) left side, affecting the jump shot attempt. Following the whistled foul, a game clock malfunction occurs. The clock is then corrected prior to Wagner's free throw attempts.
